Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:18.10,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:21.97,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Wasn't he that pirate who {\i1}failed{\i0}\Nto save his brother at Marineford?{Yeah they say "choujou sensou", which we have always translated as "the great war" here... but over time I have grown to not particularly like that translation at all so I prefer to just say Marineford personally. They both get the point across anyway. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:28.15,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,As if {\i1}not{\i0}{\fscx130} {\r}saving someone is special!  I can do that too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:35.20,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,W-W-Whad're you doin'?!  Cut i' out! {Note that due to being kinda flattened by a barrier he's having some trouble enunciating clearly. Hence the "doin'". If possible, plz add some more indicators of this. -Starfish}{ def: changing t to d represents it well but makes a bit tough to read.  just went with i' instead of it }
