Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.90,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Y-You're crushing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:48.67,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who you were just casually laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:05:00.51,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Now listen up! Straw Hat Luffy-senpai is the man\Nwho will someday stand at the very top of this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:03.25,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,He is the future Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.25,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I was there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:12.24,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,on that fateful day, over two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.10,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,In Loguetown... in the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:21.92,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,On the legendary execution stand,\Nwhere the Pirate King Roger himself died!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:25.12,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Trapped in a hopeless position, that man declared...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:29.24,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm the man who will be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.30,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,And in that moment, the heavens...{Xemnas: Never knew Dragon lived in the heavens. No wonder no one can find him.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:42.97,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,brought down the lightning, and saved him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:47.19,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I witnessed a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:55.94,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Ever since that day, I fanatically read\Neverything I could about the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:06:00.79,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Alabasta, Enies Lobby, Impel Down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:05.73,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,And last but not least,\Nthe fateful events at Marineford!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.65,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,That incident sent shivers down my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:17.52,Flashbacks,Dude,0,0,0,,Boss! What should we do\Nwith the enemy soldiers we just defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.52,Flashbacks,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Just throw'em in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:26.75,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Back where I lived, I was just a crimelord whose turf covered a measly one hundred and fifty towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.07,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I looked up to Luffy-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.51,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,And finally, I set out to sea myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.46,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Just {\i1}try{\i0}{\fscx130} {\r}to say something like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:45.32,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,You put your pathetic existence on a pedestal\Nand act like you're looking down on Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:50.00,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,What can you do?  You pathetic insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.54,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Now Bartolomeo's gone crazy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.37,Main,Cavendish,0,0,0,,Let go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.74,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why should I have to fight you in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.14,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,Hey!  Somebody stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:16.03,Main,Warrior,0,0,0,,I'm not getting involved!  It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.46,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, there's no way I could go up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.41,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I'm chickening out and losing my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:24.29,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I'm just too nervous to approach him!
