Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:06.75,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Sorry, I couldn't afford much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Thanks for treating me, Rebecca.
