Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.51,0:25:17.75,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Soldier-san is brave...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.75,0:25:22.60,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,and he will always watch over you.{Exact same phrasing as in the last episode (though he wasn't singing it there... despite the manga clearly indicating that he was supposed to be), so I copy-pasted the translation from there. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.47,0:25:25.09,Thoughts,Soldier,0,0,0,,It must be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.68,0:25:29.37,Thoughts,Soldier,0,0,0,,Though I can't feel anything with this tin body of mine. { def: brick?  any chance of tin? }{Tin indeed. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.32,0:25:35.28,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Does it feel warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.28,0:25:37.68,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Yes, it feels very warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.85,0:25:46.38,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Soldier-san is valiant...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.38,0:25:52.52,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,and he will always watch over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.20,0:25:54.92,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,How much is the rent for this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.92,0:25:57.62,Main,Old Man,0,0,0,,It's abandoned, so you can just use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.62,0:26:00.57,Main,Old Man,0,0,0,,This area was ransacked by the Riku Royal Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.57,0:26:02.51,Main,Old Man,0,0,0,,So most of the residents have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.99,0:26:05.85,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,This house is warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.85,0:26:07.08,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,You should close the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.08,0:26:07.61,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.35,0:26:11.03,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,There are toys here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.03,0:26:13.88,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Children as well. Go and play with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:18.22,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Since people are watching us in this village,\NI'll have to abide by the laws for toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.24,0:26:25.10,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,So I'll have to go to the Toys' House when you go to sleep, but I'll definitely be back before you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.33,0:26:28.47,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,As proof that I'm always by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.47,0:26:33.50,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I'll drop a single flower petal\Nthrough the gap in the window every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.28,0:26:43.88,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Good morning, Soldier-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.28,0:26:45.46,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.32,0:27:27.83,Main,Criminal,0,0,0,,She must be an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.83,0:27:29.98,Main,Criminal,0,0,0,,So the family won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.63,0:27:36.90,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.41,0:27:46.44,Main,Criminal,0,0,0,,She's pretty cute,\Nso we'll probably get a good price for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.44,0:27:48.01,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.84,0:27:59.42,Main,Criminal,0,0,0,,Damn you, how dare a toy go against humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.67,0:28:04.74,Main,Criminal,0,0,0,,I'll break you! { def: ...in half! }
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.78,0:28:10.03,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Soldier-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.22,0:28:15.39,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.82,0:28:25.00,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Forgive me. I've become a wanted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.94,0:28:27.18,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Then we're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.18,0:28:28.77,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Let's look for another house.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.62,0:28:35.59,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I want to live in the same house as you, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.81,0:28:41.83,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I'm gonna teach you how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.83,0:28:44.44,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,That's okay, I've got you to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.44,0:28:46.44,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,And what do you plan to do\Nif something happens to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.44,0:28:49.57,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Mother said that it's bad to hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.57,0:28:52.44,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,I'm teaching you this so that {\i1}you{\i0}{\fscx130} {\r}don't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.84,0:28:54.98,Main,Soldier,0,0,0,,Now come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.88,0:29:11.60,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,You were always by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:13.60,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,You protected me time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.29,0:29:21.51,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.24,0:29:25.08,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Are you ready, everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.08,0:29:28.00,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Our colosseum's very own beautiful female gladiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.00,0:29:30.47,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The phantom princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.47,0:29:34.76,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,No one gets the audience worked up like she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:38.19,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Please don't die, Soldier-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.15,0:29:41.32,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.12,0:29:45.98,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Screw you, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.98,0:29:47.85,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Today's the day you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.85,0:29:50.90,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,The entire Riku family can burn in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.90,0:29:54.07,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Your family is scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.07,0:29:55.46,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,won't lose!
